{"id": 9496, "title": "Itoshi no Betty Mamonogatari", "synopsis": "A devil-girl with the face of an angel and a heart of gold,  blond Betty falls in love with an earthbound gangster, Danpei Kimogawa, when they meet in a rainstorm. They end up living together in a Tokyo highrise apartment, though Danpei has trouble coping with his new witch and demon in-laws dropping in at inopportune moments. Betty has actually been sent to the human world on a mission to defeat the demon Lutan. While Betty continues her task, her skeletal grandmother sends nubile nymphs to tempt Danpei and see if he is suitable husband material. \n\n(Source: The Anime Encyclopedia)", "genres": [{"id": 10, "name": "Fantasy"}, {"id": 22, "name": "Romance"}, {"id": 42, "name": "Seinen"}]}